[/asy]

solution:
First we draw diagonal $\overline{BD}$, and let the diagonals intersect at $T$, as shown:


[asy]

size (4cm,4cm);

pair A,B,C,D,M;

D=(0,0);
C=(1,0);
B=(1,1);
A=(0,1);

draw(A--B--C--D--A);

M=(1/2)*D+(1/2)*C;

